Opacity tables (opacity.dat, mopacity.dat) and reemission propabilities
(ptable.dat) 

UNITS: CGS 

OH5 + MRN

* gas-to-dust ratio: 100 (so I divide OH5/100 to get cgs)  

* absorption: lambda>1 micron   -->  OH5
              lambda<1 micron   -->  MRN (after matching to OH5 at 1micron)
              lambda>1000micron -->  continue OH5  

* scattering: MRN/2

